    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The Reliable Data Protocol (RDP) is designed to provide a reliable data transport service for packet-based applications.  This RFC specifies a proposed protocol for the ARPA-Internet and DARPA research community, and requests discussion and suggestions for improvemts.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
